    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Light Nights Silent Disco</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Light Nights Silent Disco</b><br><i>Nightlife</i><br>Fri 22nd May – Fri 29th May<br>Museum of Contemporary Art, The Rocks<br>Check site<br><br>Immersive silent disco with light and sound.<br><br><a href="https://whatson.cityofsydney.nsw.gov.au/events/mca-light-nights">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
